{
  "stem": "23278.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, the one I learned in school because we were living just that close to border.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she was there, very hot, very hot.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I knew she was going to die.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so I came back two days later, because, you know, they couldn't-- we had no telephone.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the, the, the sister told me, well, she died last night.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She said, do you want to go see in the morgue which one she is?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I never seen dead people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I had to go in that morgue and lift all the, the sheets until I found her.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then we had to organize the burial.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My parents for some reason were not there, and I was the only one.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the Jewish cemetery was closed, and the Catholic cemetery would not receive anybody not Catholic.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the Protestants never were really buried.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were cremated, you know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I had to arrange that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My pastor helped me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She was in the potter's field in an unmarked grave, but we managed to have it marked, feeling that after the war, her daughter could do that, you know, and it was done.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But anyway, it's like in a French movie or the [FRENCH].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I remember that month of February, when I followed that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I don't know what you would see her, I suppose, it was an open hearse with a casket.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I guess it's OK for the orthodox Jews, just wood.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You know, making noise on the pavement, with a horse that the Germans even didn't want.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They knew the shape of the horse was all bones.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the guy was, you know, driving the horse, and me walking behind with the snow falling, and all the bells tolling because everybody was dying.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
